subject: Dear
body:
Dear

subject: Re:   Dear
body:
Hello Mr. A. Thompson,

I hope this message finds you well. I'm not sure where you heard that information, but it's always good to double-check these things, isn't it? Could you please provide more details about the fund you're referring to? 

Looking forward to your response.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Dennis
